{"tid":1208991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［求backup]宜家發生咩事 拎箱水都犯法?","createTime":"2019-06-12T10:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T19:16:39.000Z","uid":21357,"like":109,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"e92894c6bc1736c1e4e2462ac218618819b4595a","tid":1208991,"uid":21357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:39:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/279926822076021/posts/2287205284681488?s=843475231&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F279926822076021%2Fposts%2F2287205284681488%3Fs%3D843475231%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=LMVY6Z7nIekaHefcscWgVezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=ece2ee94\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/279926822076021/posts/2287205284681488?s=843475231&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n【金鐘現場】<br />\n當時一名男子攜着一箱水前行，突然十多名速龍成員不停向該男子使用胡椒噴霧及警棍，男子隨即痛苦倒地。"},{"pid":"bc4a2bdd9e258fd9e18c62c632535daaab72628d","tid":1208991,"uid":57504,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:41:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再講聽日，要就宜家！</span></span></strong><br />\n大家比人打到雞飛狗走，甘心返屋企咩！？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1208301/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1208301/page/1</a><br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所有被迫撤離嘅示威者應該尋求新戰場！</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n唔好在執着喺一個已經冇辦法抵抗，戰術價值唔大嘅地方<br />\n我地應該尋求真正威脅到政府嘅戰場！<br />\n尋晚就已經知班狗係重兵金鐘，齋屌金鐘，新界地區同埋非旺區，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">例如紅磡</span></strong>可以話係真空，而紅磡地理位置優越，鄰近<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">蝗蟲遊客聖地尖沙咀</span></strong>同<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>POLY</strong></span>，而POLY學生會照計應該會有資源支援抗爭者（唔好令我失望阿大學生）。大家應該認真諗吓！"},{"pid":"4ecb0f4b68ce5f6b486c4bea8237366e570551b7","tid":1208991,"uid":207600,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:41:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"949a4793760b51e230ba46b11f8b315359139